        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>TR has often thought naturalists do not pay enough attention to the effect of site, soil, and climate on animals and plants and "hence has arisen the enormous number of so-called species".</p>
            <p>His observations on people of different counties.</p>
